headline: Evaluating GoDaddy After 27% Drop and Strong Free Cash Flow Projections for 2025
summary: If you have been keeping tabs on GoDaddy stock lately, the decision to buy, hold, or wait might feel anything but straightforward. On one hand, the past three years have given investors an impressive 91.1% return, and over five years, shares are up 93.5%. However, a closer look at the shorter-term picture tells a different story: down 3.2% in just the last week, off 1.2% over the past month, and a significant drop of 27.5% year-to-date.
